<h1 id="manage-leave-and-absence-requests" sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="32">Manage leave and absence requests</h1>

<p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Managers can manage time-off requests from the <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="34">Employee self service</strong> workspace in Dynamics 365 Human Resources. Requests can be simple single-day requests or multiple-day requests that include multiple leave and absence types. If a workflow isn't enabled, the requests are automatically approved. If a workflow is enabled, the approval can be automatic, or it can require sign-off, depending on the workflow configuration.</p>
<ol sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">In the <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">Employee self service</strong> workspace, select <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="36">My team</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Under <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">My team information</strong>, select the <strong sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="38">Leave and absence</strong> tab.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40"><p sourcefile="human-resources/hr-employee-self-service-manage-requests.md" sourcestartlinenumber="40">View and approve your team members' time-off requests as necessary.</p>
</li>
</ol>
